  featureName: Quick Validation
  shortDescription: Detect common setup issues before runtime.
  fullDescription: "Trailback Quick Validation performs a fast health check of common
    framework components and configuration mistakes.\r\n\r\nChecks include:\r\n\r\n\u2022
    Missing Components\r\n\u2022 Duplicate Components\r\n\u2022 Disabled Components\r\n\r\nValidation
    results are displayed directly in the Unity Console and include object references
    to help locate problems quickly.\r\n\r\nDesigned to catch common setup mistakes
    before they become runtime issues and reduce integration time during development."
  screenshots: []
